<sentence id="4">To test for continued H4 acetylation in metaphase chromosomes .</sentence>
<sentence id="5">Chinese hamster ovary cells were blocked in metaphase and treated for one hour with the deacetylase inhibitor sodium butyrate .</sentence>
<sentence id="6">Isolated chromosomes were assayed for H4 acetylation by antibody labeling and flow cytometry .</sentence>
